languages.en: //(0,5.4)\\I suppose. I think the problem is that it’s hard to see the bigger picture sometimes.//(5.4,8.3)\\Hard to know exactly where, or what we’re doing.//(8.3,38.3)\\I suppose I just have to trust that the people who see the big picture know that it’s right.
languages.fr: //(0,1.86)\\Je crois, oui.//(1.86,5.47)\\Je pense que j'ai du mal à distinguer notre but ultime.//(5.47,9.05)\\C'est difficile de savoir où on va et ce qu'on fait.//(9.05,39.05)\\Je devrais faire confiance aux gens qui connaissent exactement tous les enjeux.
languages.it: //(0,5.371)\\Forse sì. Il problema è che a volte è difficile capire quale sia il piano.//(5.371,9.030062)\\Sapere di preciso cosa stiamo facendo.//(9.030062,39.03006)\\Immagino che dovrei fidarmi del giudizio di chi ha una prospettiva più ampia.
languages.de: //(0,5.7)\\Wahrscheinlich. Das Problem ist, dass es manchmal schwer ist, das große Ganze zu sehen.//(5.7,9.1)\\Ich weiß nicht genau, was wir eigentlich machen.//(9.1,39.1)\\Vermutlich muss ich darauf vertrauen, dass die Leute, die das große Ganze sehen, schon wissen werden, dass das alles richtig ist.
languages.es: //(0,5.5)\\Supongo que sí. Creo que el problema es que a veces cuesta ver el plan en su conjunto.//(5.5,8.902)\\Es difícil saber exactamente qué estamos haciendo.//(8.902,38.902)\\Supongo que tengo que confiar en que la gente que sí puede verlo sepa qué es lo correcto.
languages.ru: //(0,1.506196)\\Да, наверное...//(1.506196,5.55)\\Думаю, проблема в том, что иногда я не вижу всей картины целиком.//(5.55,8.85)\\Сложно понять, что и зачем мы делаем.//(8.85,38.85)\\Наверное, надо просто довериться тем, кто это знает.
languages.cn: //(0,5.4)\\我想是的。我觉得问题在于，有时我们很难看清大局。//(5.4,8.3)\\很难知道我们到底在哪里，在做什么。//(8.3,38.3)\\我想，我只能相信，那些洞察全局的人知道这样做是对的。
languages.tc: //(0,5.4)\\我想。我認為問題在於有時很難看到更大的圖像。//(5.4,8.3)\\很難確切地知道我們在哪裡，或者我們在做什麼。//(8.3,38.3)\\我想我只需要相信那些看到大局的人就知道這是正確的。
languages.jp: //(0,5.4)\\I suppose. I think the problem is that it’s hard to see the bigger picture sometimes.//(5.4,8.3)\\Hard to know exactly where, or what we’re doing.//(8.3,38.3)\\I suppose I just have to trust that the people who see the big picture know that it’s right.
